jacobiano\SpecialChar ~
de\SpecialChar ~

\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset 

 denotado a veces 
\begin_inset Formula \[
J\left[f\left[x^{1}\ldots x^{n}\right]\right]=\frac{\partial\left(f^{1}\ldots f^{k}\right)}{\partial\left(x^{1}\ldots x^{n}\right)}\]

\end_inset 

se calcula así: 
\begin_inset Formula \[
J\left[f\left[x^{1}\ldots x^{n}\right]\right]=\left|\begin{array}{ccc}
\dpa{f^{1}}{x^{1}} & \ldots & \dpa{f^{1}}{x^{n}}\\
\vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
\dpa{f^{k}}{x^{1}} & \ldots & \dpa{f^{k}}{x^{n}}\end{array}\right|\]

